rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Superbia and Invidia... When those
two go to war, there's no doubt Gula
will be caught in the middle.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0002
rows.name:
But Gula itself has no power
to fight. We'll simply be ruled
by the victorious nation.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0003
rows.name:
All we can do is pray that
the winner won't let Gula's
civilization be trampled.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0004
rows.name:
The best thing would be for this
war to never happen, and for
things to stay as they are...
